      "translations": {
        "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
          "Hadith.2866 - Mu'awiyah ibn Ammar asked Abu Abdullah (as) about a man who performed Hajj on behalf of someone else: \"Does it suffice for him as his Hajj of Islam?\"\nImam (as) replied: \"Yes.\""
